dev.aherscu.qa.jgiven.commons.utils

Class DbUnitExModule

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.unitils.dbunit.DbUnitModule
      • dev.aherscu.qa.jgiven.commons.utils.DbUnitExModule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.unitils.core.Module

    public class DbUnitExModule
extends org.unitils.dbunit.DbUnitModule
    Provides data insertion method using the default dataset factory.

    In order to use this class during runtime, the unitils.properties file of the project shall contain unitils.module.dbunit.className=DbUnitExModule .

    Author:
    aherscu
